org.beryx.streamplify.combination

Class LongCombinations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.LongIndexedSpliterator<int[],LongCombinations>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.combination.LongCombinations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Spliterator<int[]>, Streamable<int[],LongCombinations>

    public class LongCombinations
extends LongIndexedSpliterator<int[],LongCombinations>
    Provides streams of combinations.
    Can be used when the binomial coefficient (n choose k) is a number that can fit in a long. For bigger values, a BigIntegerCombinations is needed.
